            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\[\n\\begin{array}{l} \\therefore d T = k L \\frac {d ^ {2} r}{d x ^ {2}} d x \\\\ \\therefore k L \\frac {d ^ {2} r}{d x ^ {2}} d x = - \\frac {m}{L} d x w _ {1} ^ {2} r \\\\ \\mathrm {即} \\frac {d ^ {2} r}{d x ^ {2}} = - \\frac {z ^ {2}}{9} \\frac {r}{L ^ {2}} \\\\ \\therefore \\frac {d r ^ {1}}{d r} r ^ {1} = - \\frac {\\pi^ {2}}{9} \\frac {r}{l ^ {2}} \\Rightarrow 3 r ^ {1 2} = - \\frac {\\pi^ {2}}{9} \\frac {r ^ {2}}{l ^ {2}} + C _ {1} \\\\ \\end{array}\n\\]"
